#: resources/ui/overlays.ui:140 resources/ui/panel.ui:101
msgid "Radius for the corner rounding effect."
msgstr ""

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:149
msgid "Enable corner rounding on maximized and fullscreen"
msgstr ""

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:150
msgid ""
"Corner rounding effect will keep being applied to maximized and fullscreen "
"windows."
msgstr ""

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:164
msgid "Opacity"
msgstr "불투명도"

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:165
msgid ""
"The opacity of the window on top of the blur effect, a higher value will be "
"more legible."
msgstr "블러 효과 외에도 창의 불투명도는 값이 높을수록 읽기 쉽습니다."

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:186
msgid "Opaque focused window"
msgstr "불투명한 포커스 창"

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:187
msgid ""
"Makes the focused window opaque and the other ones blurred, helping with "
"legibility."
msgstr "포커스 창은 불투명하게, 다른 창은 블러해서 가독성을 높입니다."

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:201
msgid "Blur on overview"
msgstr "오버뷰 모드 블러"

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:202
msgid ""
"Forces the blur to be properly shown on all workspaces on overview.\n"
"This may cause some latency or performance issues."
msgstr ""
"오버뷰 모드의 모든 작업 공간에서 블러 효과가 제대로 표시되도록 합니다.\n"
"이로 인해 지연 시간이나 성능 문제가 발생할 수 있습니다."

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:217
msgid "Enable all by default"
msgstr "기본적으로 모두 활성화"

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:218
msgid "Adds blur behind all windows by default."
msgstr "기본적으로 모든 창 뒤에 블러 효과를 추가합니다."

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:234
msgid "Whitelist"
msgstr "화이트리스트"

#: resources/ui/applications.ui:235
msgid ""
"A list of windows to blur.\n"
"Use * to match any sequence of characters (e.g., Firefox* or *Code*), and ? "
"for a single one."
msgstr ""

